OL,3,CAutistic girl died during trip with
OL,4,Cchildminder, inquest told
OL,6,FA seven-year-old autistic girl
OL,7,Fdisappeared while out with a
OL,8,Fchildminder before being found
OL,9,Funresponsive in a pond on a golf
OL,10,Fcourse, an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FNyla May Bradshaw died at Doncaster
OL,13,FRoyal Infirmary on 30 March after she
OL,14,Fwas pulled from the water at Owston
OL,15,FGolf Course, north of Doncaster, South
OL,16,FYorkshire.
OL,18,FThe inquest opening on Thursday heard
OL,19,FNyla was non-verbal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
