OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776041694
OL,3,CAutistic girl died during trip with
OL,4,Cchildminder, inquest told
OL,6,FCoroner's officer Jane McDonnell said
OL,7,Fshe was being looked after by a
OL,8,Fchildminder and "during the course of
OL,9,Fthe day she was taken out to a park in
OL,10,Fthe Owston area of Doncaster".
OL,12,FShe said: "During the course of the
OL,13,Fexcursion she passed through a gap in
OL,14,Fthe fence and approached woodland
OL,15,Fclose to Owston Golf Course."
OL,17,FMs McDonnell said a search began after
OL,18,Fthe childminder raised the alarm with
OL,19,Fpolice and Nyla's family.
OL,26,@pD@QOUrD@]O]tD@KOUwD@]O]
