OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776041694
OL,3,CAutistic girl died during trip with
OL,4,Cchildminder, inquest told
OL,6,FThe girl was found unresponsive and
OL,7,Fface down in a pond on the golf
OL,8,Fcourse, the officer told Doncaster's
OL,9,Fsenior coroner Nicola Mundy.
OL,11,FNyla was taken to hospital but could
OL,12,Fbe resuscitated, the court heard.
OL,14,FMs Mundy fixed a provisional inquest
OL,15,Fdate for 8 December.
OL,17,FNo cause of death was given during the
OL,18,Ffive-minute hearing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
