CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776041694
OL,3,CAutistic girl died during trip with
OL,4,Cchildminder, inquest told
OL,6,FNo members of Nyla's family were at
OL,7,Fthe hearing but the coroner asked for
OL,8,Fthem to kept informed of the
OL,9,Fproceedings.
OL,11,FAfter her death, children's autism
OL,12,Fcharity Little Rainbows Doncaster
OL,13,Fsaid: "Nyla was a beautiful, deeply
OL,14,Floved seven-year-old girl who brought
OL,15,Fso much light to those around her."
OL,17,FIt said "her presence spoke volumes".
OL,26,@uD@GOU
