PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776041694
OL,3,CAutistic girl died during trip with
OL,4,Cchildminder, inquest told
OL,6,F"She touched more lives than words
OL,7,Fcould ever express. A beautiful little
OL,8,Fgirl who loved Christmas especially,"
OL,9,Fit said.
OL,11,F"Our entire community is heartbroken,
OL,12,Fand our thoughts are firmly with her
OL,13,Ffamily as they face this unimaginable
OL,14,Floss."
OL,16,FThe charity added: "For many of us as
OL,17,Fparents of autistic children, this is
OL,18,Fthe fear we carry every single day `
OL,19,Fand today, that fear has become a
OL,20,Freality for one of our own."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@FO]xD@TOU|D@\O]
