OL,3,CAutistic girl died during trip with
OL,4,Cchildminder, inquest told
OL,6,FLittle Rainbows later issued a
OL,7,Fstatement saying Nyla's death
OL,8,Fhighlighted "the systemic issues that
OL,9,Fmay have contributed to the
OL,10,Fcircumstances in which this incident
OL,11,Foccurred".
OL,13,FAn online tribute page was set up
OL,14,Fafter the tragedy which has raised
OL,15,Fmore than #20,000 to help Nyla's
OL,16,Ffamily with the funeral and other
OL,17,Fcosts.
OL,26,@pD@MOUsD@IO]
